Explanation
 
BACKGROUND:
This ordinance approves the acceptance of certain territory (AN23-014) by the city of Columbus. The Ohio Revised Code stipulates that to be effective, City acceptance must take place a minimum of 60 days from the receipt by the City Clerk of the approval notice from the county. If City Council does not accept the ordinance within 120 days of its first consideration, the annexation will be considered rejected. This petition was filed with Franklin County on June 14, 2023. City Council approved a service ordinance addressing the site on June 26, 2023. Franklin County approved the annexation on July 18, 2023 and the City Clerk received notice on July 28, 2023.
FISCAL IMPACT:
Provision of municipal services does represent cost to the City; however, the annexation of land also has the potential to create revenue to the City.
 
 
Title
 
To accept the application (AN23-014) of 4747 Dublin Road LLC for the annexation of certain territory containing 6.1± acres in Norwich Township.
 
 
Body
 
WHEREAS, a petition for the annexation of certain territory in Norwich Township was filed on behalf of 4747 Dublin Road LLC on June 14, 2023; and
WHEREAS, the petition was considered and approved by the Franklin County Board of Commissioners at a hearing on July 18, 2023; and
WHEREAS, on July 28, 2023, the City Clerk received from Franklin County a certified copy of the resolution addressing the petition; and
WHEREAS, sixty days have now elapsed since receipt of the resolution in accordance with the provisions of the Ohio Revised Code; and
WHEREAS, it is in the best interest of the city of Columbus to accept the annexation of the territory addressed by the petition; NOW, THEREFORE,
BE IT ORDAINED BY THE COUNCIL OF THE CITY OF COLUMBUS
SECTION 1. That the annexation proposed by 4747 Dublin Road LLC in a petition filed with the Franklin County Board of Commissioners on June 14, 2023 and subsequently approved by the Board on July 18, 2023 is hereby accepted and said territory is hereby annexed to the city of Columbus. Said territory is described as follows:
